			<h4><a name="2775850">Ion Dallas</a></h4>


		 	<span id="comment_score_2775850" class="score">(Score:1)</span>
		</div>
		<div class="details">
			by <a href="//slashdot.org/~AbortRetryIgnore">AbortRetryIgnore (547508)</a> 
			<span class="otherdetails" id="comment_otherdetails_2775850">		
		on Wednesday January 02, @06:17PM (<a href="//slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=25551&amp;cid=2775850">#2775850</a>)
