			<h4><a name="2777643">Re:Comments</a></h4>


		 	<span id="comment_score_2777643" class="score">(Score:1)</span>
		</div>
		<div class="details">
			by <a href="//slashdot.org/~Julian+K">Julian K (547604)</a> 
			<span class="otherdetails" id="comment_otherdetails_2777643">		
		on Thursday January 03, @02:54AM (<a href="//slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=25551&amp;cid=2777643">#2777643</a>)
		<small> </small>
